{"tid":2515631,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新一代疫苗可能是藥丸或噴霧式","createTime":"2021-05-04T06:24:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T06:55:31.000Z","uid":73071,"like":11,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"70f72ce2dd81eb1696ed31ab1fbb455dc1214d18","tid":2515631,"uid":73071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:24:37.000Z","msg":"&quot;《華爾街日報》報道，研究中的新疫苗毋須用針更易接種，亦可望減少低溫儲存等的限制，更易運送到鄉郊地區存放使用。<br />\n<br />\n美國公司Altimmune研發中的噴鼻式疫苗，採用改造過的腺病毒，設計與強生和阿斯利康的疫苗差不多，但噴鼻式疫苗可以誘導身體產生黏膜免疫力，有助清除在呼吸道的病毒。公司期望在年中公布早期臨床試驗的結果，屆時會知道疫苗能否安全誘導免疫反應。<br />\n<br />\n另一間總部設於美國加州南三藩市的公司Vaxart，就正研發藥丸式疫苗，公司二月時表示，早期的小型臨床試驗顯示，能有效誘發免疫反應，並期望年中開展第二階段臨床試驗。<br />\n<br />\n隨著變種新冠病毒出現，藥廠輝瑞和莫德納都針對變種病毒，研發第二代疫苗。&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=433503\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433503&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnuIs%2Fr43DZ9KHrtYDEqBsnw%3D&h=1ab5b79e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D433503&h=6a19d36f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=433503</a>"},{"pid":"34a65b2390f40ec3061d35cd33a1b4b0797ab3cb","tid":2515631,"uid":127905,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:25:39.000Z","msg":"藥丸式<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7d06fa1315a9834d2dff3fd213d95766ac897aa","tid":2515631,"uid":275498,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"口服既 副作用係咪 無咁多 ? <br />\n<br />\nbewteen,  第二代點都應該低風險過第一次吧"},{"pid":"0c85d915000e20c806d430ca1a11bbf72b28aaeb","tid":2515631,"uid":66324,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T06:27:31.000Z","msg":"&quot;改造過的腺病毒&quot;<br />\n肺向栓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src